                        <svg class="absolute left-0 top-0 md:top-1 z-30" width="77" height="35" viewBox="0 0 77 35" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">
